{"tid":246970,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)獅子王1-3","createTime":"2017-05-17T12:02:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-17T15:42:01.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bfea0e6d51401c01ee859e8879e5b15027d3b96e","tid":246970,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T12:02:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2F&d=Ur8nmiChwnCvVlPnSGk5XgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=e3e5c0f1\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/</a> CC台又執柒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=Ur8nmiChwnCvVlPnSGk5XgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=94c06c9b\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=Ur8nmiChwnCvVlPnSGk5XgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=f9fb7706\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"http://vignette3.wikia.nocookie.net/vocustaiwan/images/c/c1/%E7%8D%85%E5%AD%90%E7%8E%8B.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20150804043653&amp;path-prefix=zh\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvignette3.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fvocustaiwan%2Fimages%2Fc%2Fc1%2F%25E7%258D%2585%25E5%25AD%2590%25E7%258E%258B.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20150804043653%26path-prefix%3Dzh&h=8a5a81b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.在廣闊的非洲草原上，動物們聚集在獅王木法沙的榮耀石下，迎接新王子誕生。狒狒巫師拉飛奇高舉起一隻好奇的新生命&mdash;&mdash;辛巴，動物們紛紛向其致意，全國一片歡騰的景象，只有木法沙的兄弟刀疤對此很不滿意，甚至沒有出席這場儀式。<br />\n時光飛逝，年幼的辛巴在成長，他對世界好奇而充滿幻想，而刀疤始終都想篡奪兄長的王位，他鼓勵辛巴去大象墓地探險證實自己的勇氣，然後指示一群土狼手下乘機襲擊。但沒想到木法沙及時出現，趕走了土狼..<br />\n<br />\n2.故事講述辛巴和娜娜誕下女兒琪拉雅。而刀疤的妻子吉娜一心報複，她向自己和另一隻獅子誕下的兒子高孚灌入壞思想，要他殺死辛巴。誰知琪拉雅和高孚相戀，他們要化解上一代的恩怨，他們的愛情才有好結果......<br />\n<br />\n3.在距離榮耀石（Pride Rock）很遠的地方，是狐獴丁滿（Timon）的家鄉。丁滿被指派為挖掘工以及守衛，但是丁滿什麼事情都辦不好，在差點讓自己的親戚被土狼桑琪（Shenzi）、阿德（Ed）、和班仔（Banzai）吃掉的情況下，他決定離開家鄉，去為自己找一個歸屬之地。於是在狒狒拉飛奇（Rafiki）的鼓勵下，丁滿就往榮耀石前進了。在旅途上，丁滿遇見了疣豬彭彭（Pumbaa），並決定一同尋找一塊安身之地.....<br />\n<br />\n8 40PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"711bbcf1e995c01f57c34dcdd524cfed19f5c30a","tid":246970,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T12:03:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6744e56148fa38f8fcf76ce8188f849fba66dffa","tid":246970,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T12:50:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f997fc190b3d0c69a9040c121a0de5cd4e7e799b","tid":246970,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T13:06:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bbc4086181de0af9d7a74364c2439be03b1ebce","tid":246970,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T13:32:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5625682fdf72a3f5901de58255f7096120d65ab","tid":246970,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T13:51:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"401dea0c0c37cc447f8b51802d49a320ead6735a","tid":246970,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T14:14:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38fe42a28a29b1002bfa8bf8a6b1fbad3ebe48e8","tid":246970,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T14:37:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17748ea54914a58f195f7aca58c7fcb766c07354","tid":246970,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T15:01:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c73cc8d670b29ca90d698d6b5d2e4e0b6b5b5e3","tid":246970,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T15:29:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2965bcda8dd48ec66c2eef83d371a575679b5250","tid":246970,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T15:42:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}